---
title: Maple-Glazed Pork Chops with Wild Rice   and Roasted Squash, Apple and Kale Salad
description: Get ready to experience the flavours of fall! Juicy, maple-glazed pork chops are seared to perfection and served alongside creamy wild rice. Roasted squash, apple and kale salad topped with toasted pumpkin seeds brings satisfying crunch.

